    <h1 class="mb-6">AI SEO Agency Services</h1>
    <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mb-8">By Adam Parker | Updated April 2026</p>

    <div class="bg-off-white border-l-3 border-l-teal rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
      <p class="text-[15px] text-teal font-medium leading-relaxed m-0">A transparent breakdown of exactly what you get when you invest in our local SEO services, from month one audits to ongoing optimization.</p>
    </div>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">You want to know exactly what you're paying for. Fair enough. Here's precisely what happens when you hire us, month by month.</p>

<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Month 1: Foundation and Quick Wins</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">We start with a comprehensive local SEO audit. This isn't a generic checklist. We examine your Google Business Profile, local citations, website technical health, and competitor landscape. You'll get a detailed report within the first week.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Next, we establish your baseline. We document current rankings, traffic patterns, and conversion data. This becomes our benchmark for measuring success.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Then we implement quick wins. These are high-impact changes that often show results within weeks. We optimise your Google Business Profile, fix critical NAP inconsistencies, and address urgent technical issues.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">By month's end, you'll have access to your custom dashboard, showing real-time rankings and traffic data. No waiting for monthly reports to see what's happening.</p>

<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Months 2-3: Building Your Local Ecosystem</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">This is where we build the foundation for long-term success. We create and optimise citations across 50+ relevant directories and platforms. Not just the obvious ones like Yelp, but industry-specific directories that actually matter for your business.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">We develop your content strategy. This includes location-specific landing pages, service area pages, and regular blog content that targets local search terms. Every piece is written by experienced copywriters, not AI or juniors.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Technical fixes happen during this phase. We address site speed issues, mobile responsiveness problems, and schema markup implementation. These changes improve both user experience and search engine understanding.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Review generation systems go live. We implement processes to encourage genuine customer reviews across Google, industry platforms, and social media. This isn't about buying fake reviews. It's about making it easier for happy customers to share their experience.</p>

<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Month 4 and Beyond: Optimisation and Growth</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Now we focus on continuous improvement. We monitor rankings daily and adjust strategies based on performance data. Google's algorithm changes constantly, and we adapt accordingly.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Content creation continues with monthly blog posts, updated service pages, and seasonal campaigns. We track which content drives leads and double down on what works.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Citation monitoring becomes crucial. We watch for new opportunities, fix any NAP inconsistencies that appear, and maintain your online reputation across all platforms.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Monthly strategy calls keep you informed. We discuss performance, upcoming changes, and new opportunities. You'll always know what we're working on and why.</p>

<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Complete Deliverables List</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">• 24/7 dashboard access showing rankings, traffic, and leads<br>
• Monthly performance reviews with actionable insights<br>
• Quarterly citation audit reports<br>
• Complete local ecosystem build (50+ citations)<br>
• Custom content strategy and implementation<br>
• Google Business Profile optimisation and management<br>
• Technical SEO fixes and ongoing monitoring<br>
• Review generation system setup<br>
• Competitor analysis and market insights<br>
• Direct access to senior team members</p>

<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">What You Don't Get</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">No junior staff working on your account. Every client gets senior-level expertise from day one.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">No generic SEO tactics. We don't do national SEO, PPC management, or social media marketing. We focus exclusively on local search.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">No fluff reports. Our reporting shows business metrics that matter: rankings, traffic, leads, and revenue. No vanity metrics or industry jargon.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">No long-term contracts. We earn your business every month through results, not legal obligations.</p>

<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Investment Levels</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5"><strong>Essential:</strong> £1,500/month - Perfect for single-location businesses targeting one primary service area. Includes all core services with monthly content creation.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5"><strong>Growth:</strong> £2,500/month - Ideal for businesses with multiple services or targeting several locations. Includes advanced content strategy and competitive analysis.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5"><strong>Dominate:</strong> £4,000/month - For businesses serious about market leadership. Includes aggressive content creation, advanced technical optimisation, and priority support.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">All plans include the complete deliverables list above. The difference is scope and intensity.</p>

<h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Ready to Start?</h2>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Book a strategy call to discuss which approach fits your business goals. Or request a free local SEO audit to see exactly where you stand today.</p>

<p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Either way, you'll get specific recommendations for your situation. No sales pressure, just honest advice about what it takes to dominate local search in your market.</p>

